@startuml
autonumber
actor "Maintenance Supervisor" as MS
participant "MaintenanceController" as Ctrl
participant "ViewTotalMaintenanceHoursInFleetUseCase" as UC
participant "MaintenanceRecordRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

MS -> Ctrl : GET /api/maintenance/records/hours
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC : execute()
activate UC

UC -> Repo : findAll()
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT FROM maintenance_record
activate DB
DB --> Repo : list of records
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC : List<MaintenanceRecord>
deactivate Repo

note right of UC
  Sums expectedDuration (in hours)
  across all maintenance records
  in the fleet
end note

UC --> Ctrl : ViewTotalMaintenanceHoursInFleetResponse\n{ totalHours: Integer }
deactivate UC

Ctrl --> MS : 200 OK\nEntityModel<ViewTotalMaintenanceHoursInFleetResponse>\nwith _links (self)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml
